        "authorId" : "fa18c2b0-9128-4c2b-b6e0-433b177f7cf1",
        "body" : "Can you add a `recipe/conda_build_config.yaml` with,\r\n\r\n```yaml\r\nCUDA_VER:\r\n  - 9.2\r\n  - 10.0\r\n```\r\nand use the value like `set version = CUDA_VER`",
        "createdAt" : "2019-08-15T22:34:55Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2019-08-16T19:05:47Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "fa18c2b0-9128-4c2b-b6e0-433b177f7cf1",
        "tags" : [
        ]
