      {
        "id" : "de6619bf-e4f0-468f-8de6-91a3941583b3",
        "parentId" : "179e86c4-e1d6-4c9a-a89c-70cefc114116",
        "authorId" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "body" : "The `9.2` is really only here to make the linter happy. Personally I'd rather not have it here at all if it could be avoided.\r\n\r\nBasically what this is doing is picking up [`CUDA_VER` from the docker image]( https://github.com/conda-forge/docker-images/blob/2a183bf61c0db6a7c352da0c757717b33d8fd87e/linux-anvil-cuda/Dockerfile#L9 ).",
        "createdAt" : "2019-08-15T22:40:20Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2019-08-16T19:05:47Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "tags" : [
        ]
      }
